{"type": "article", "id": 40018, "title": "纽约时装周要缩短一天日程 ，以及，推荐一个浸染风的丹麦牛仔品牌｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-04-21T03:30:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 2041, "name": "Jimmy Choo"}, {"id": 5498, "name": "Cartier"}, {"id": 7048, "name": "纽约时装周"}, {"id": 14244, "name": "浮华日报"}, {"id": 39687, "name": "Won Hundred"}, {"id": 39688, "name": "Building Block"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170421112417njMd5u6zF7EcGsWX.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.wmagazine.com/story/new-york-fashion-week-shortens-schedule\" rel=\"nofollow\">纽约时装周要缩短一天日程</a>&nbsp;</strong><strong>| </strong>有 8天的纽约时装周要缩短日程，变成真正的时装“周”了。Marc Jacobs 和&nbsp;Calvin Klein 会去 ，<a href=\"http://www.wmagazine.com/story/proenza-schouler-ditches-new-york-fashion-week-for-haute-couture\" rel=\"nofollow\">Proenza Schouler</a>&nbsp;则要去巴黎时装周，而&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.wmagazine.com/story/gigi-hadid-tommy-hilfiger-lady-gaga-fashion-show-venice-beach-california\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tommy Hilfiger</a>&nbsp;和 Rebecca Minkoff 则直接在洛杉矶走秀了。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Estee-Lauder-unveils-virtual-makeup-app-in-stores-across-the-UK,818640.html#.WPl071K758c\" rel=\"nofollow\">雅诗兰黛开始在英国的店里用上了 VR 技术</a> </strong><strong>|&nbsp;</strong>简单说来就是对着“墨镜”就能轻松试口红。这次雅诗兰黛是和美妆 APP&nbsp;YouCam 合作。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>丹麦牛仔品牌&nbsp;<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2017/4/won-hundred-2017-spring-90s-denim-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Won Hundred&nbsp;</a>以 90 年代为灵感做的新系列，可以看到磨损和过度浸染的风格。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017042110213827nYFEoPUgducat0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421102150cBymHavtI1VlWun9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421102205s8lUIE3Jot0qBrM4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421102215rByDHh49Cb7NVRPL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p class=\"\">Jimmy Choo 2017 早秋系列的广告。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421092552qLXRbBrlQzhVu3OM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421092610PC5AVqxDTFIQUpZr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421092559D8vYqCbg7NR2h53M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421092626zNgcuqWvL3aPBV29.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421092648pSDL4fu2JeK3Hdic.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p><br></p><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/cartier-juste-un-clou-new-release\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cartier 推出升级版的 Juste un Clou 系列</a>。简单说来，就是把“钉子”的部分放大了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421100100JlWtpKcs8qvGaMmC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421100109FnuTQK2IyxzdeMVP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421100127umG5kIrFc4Pn2t8D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421100045iksVqwPYheSD6Zul.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p><br></p><p>洛杉矶的手袋品牌&nbsp;<a href=\"https://building--block.com/products\" rel=\"nofollow\">Building Block</a>&nbsp;又推了新款，依旧极简风、这次还用上了 PVC 的透明材质，适合夏天。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421104326HNMV4okJTgvanKF1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.414169\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421104337RHecvCIFBAN1O0ys.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.351563\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421104405p0swUaC7fYSitMnV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459384\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421104416yqDOS8MwszZpBnx5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421104351T7Eki0ZloqMLKHO4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.406504\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421104445z1eTCDdbZSPu8HyM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.439560\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421104432gpVPtrJMCHou8NqR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170421113412Gze08uw3xAVKQcm4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.443182\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"